quran[21{c,v,t}:
54,7,khushsha'an absaaruhum yakrujoona minal ajdaasi ka annahum jaraadum muntashir
54,8,Muhti'eena ilad daa'i yaqoolul kafiroona haazaa yawmun 'asir
54,9,Kazzabat qablahum qawmu Noohin fakazzaboo 'abdanaa wa qaaloo majnoo nunw wazdujir
54,10,Fada'aa Rabbahooo annee maghloobun fantasir
54,11,Fafatahnaaa abwaabas sa maaa'i bimaa'im munhamir
54,12,Wa fajjamal arda 'uyoonan faltaqal maaa'u 'alaaa amrin qad qudir
54,13,Wa hamalnaahu 'alaa zaati alwaahinw wa dusur
54,14,Tajree bi a'yuninaa jazaaa 'al liman kaana kufir
54,15,Wa laqat taraknaahaad aayatan fahal mim muddakir
54,16,Fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
54,17,Wa laqad yassamal Quraana liz zikri fahal mimmuddakir
54,18,Kazzabat 'Aadun fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
54,19,Innaa arsalnaa 'alaihim reehan sarsaran fee Yawmi nahsim mustamirr
54,20,Tanzi;un naasa ka anna huma'jaazu nakhlim munqa'ir
54,21,'Fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
54,22,Wa laqad yassamal Quraana liz zikri fahal mim muddakir
54,23,Kazzabat Samoodu binnuzur
54,24,Faqaalooo a-basharam minnaa waahidan nattabi'uhooo innaa izal lafee dalaalinw wa su'ur
54,25,'A-ulqiyaz zikru 'alaihi mim baininaa bal huwa kazzaabun ashir
54,26,Sa-ya'lamoona ghadam manil kazzaabul ashir
54,27,Innaa mursilun naaqati fitnatal lahum fartaqibhum wastabir
